          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " For the capture measurements were used 11.05-g of",
                "  99.3% Kr-82 enriched gas, 17.35-g of 99.5% Kr-84",
                " enriched gas and 18.03-g of 99.9% Kr-86 enriched gas.",
                " In addition, three other samples were prepared, one",
                " filled with N(2) to be used as a dummy sample,",
                "in order to clearly identify all the structures due to",
                "the alloy of the container. Another one was filled with",
                "natural xenon and used for normalization purposes and",
                "a last one was filled with 25.87-g of natural krypton."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*.In order to improve the uncertainty on the",
                "normalization, was performed a dedicated total cross",
                "section measurement using a natural xenon sample.",
                "Subsequently the data have been normalized using three",
                "different resonances of Xe-131. The three obtained",
                "normalisation factors agreed within 1% and the averaged",
                "value was then adopted."
              ]
            }
          ],
